  "id": "api/common/CurrencyPipe",
  "title": "CurrencyPipe",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L95-L163\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.7/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L95-L163\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/CurrencyPipe\", \"name\": \"CurrencyPipe\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"currencypipe\">CurrencyPipe<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#currencypipe\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p>Uses the functions <a href=\"api/common/getCurrencySymbol\"><code>getCurrencySymbol</code></a> and <a href=\"api/common/formatCurrency\"><code>formatCurrency</code></a> to format a\nnumber as currency using locale rules.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  \n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>Use <code>currency</code> to format a number as currency.</p>\n<p>Where:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>value</code> is a number.</li>\n<li><code>currencyCode</code> is the <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a> currency code, such\nas <code>USD</code> for the US dollar and <code>EUR</code> for the euro.</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>display</code> indicates whether to show the currency symbol, the code or a custom value:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>code</code>: use code (e.g. <code>USD</code>).</li>\n<li><code>symbol</code>(default): use symbol (e.g. <code>$</code>).</li>\n<li><code>symbol-narrow</code>: some countries have two symbols for their currency, one regular and one\nnarrow (e.g. the canadian dollar CAD has the symbol <code>CA$</code> and the symbol-narrow <code>$</code>).</li>\n<li><code>string</code>: use this value instead of a code or a symbol.</li>\n<li>boolean (deprecated from v5): <code>true</code> for symbol and false for <code>code</code>.\nIf there is no narrow symbol for the chosen currency, the regular symbol will be used.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><code>digitInfo</code> See <a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a> for more details.</li>\n<li><code>locale</code> is a <code>string</code> defining the locale to use (uses the current <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> by\ndefault).</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"example\">Example<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#example\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'currency-pipe',\n  template: `&#x3C;div>\n    &#x3C;!--output '$0.259'-->\n    &#x3C;p>A: {{<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> | currency}}&#x3C;/p>\n\n    &#x3C;!--output 'CA$0.26'-->\n    &#x3C;p>A: {{<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> | currency:'CAD'}}&#x3C;/p>\n\n    &#x3C;!--output 'CAD0.26'-->\n    &#x3C;p>A: {{<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> | currency:'CAD':'code'}}&#x3C;/p>\n\n    &#x3C;!--output 'CA$0,001.35'-->\n    &#x3C;p>B: {{b | currency:'CAD':'symbol':'4.2-2'}}&#x3C;/p>\n\n    &#x3C;!--output '$0,001.35'-->\n    &#x3C;p>B: {{b | currency:'CAD':'symbol-narrow':'4.2-2'}}&#x3C;/p>\n\n    &#x3C;!--output '0 001,35 CA$'-->\n    &#x3C;p>B: {{b | currency:'CAD':'symbol':'4.2-2':'fr'}}&#x3C;/p>\n  &#x3C;/div>`\n})\nexport class CurrencyPipeComponent {\n  <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a>: number = 0.259;\n  b: number = 1.3495;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage Notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p><code>number_expression | currency[:currencyCode[:display[:digitInfo[:locale]]]]</code></p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - guide/i18n\n - guide/pipes\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#currencypipe\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#description\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#example\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#usage-notes\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/formatCurrency\n - api/common/getCurrencySymbol\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L95-L163\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0-beta.7/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L95-L163\n-->"
